---
// landing_page/src/components/home/DualPath.astro

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');---
<section class="relative border-t border-line">
  <div class="container-page py-28 md:py-36">
    <div class="max-w-2xl reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow-signal">[ 03 / ENGAGE ]</p>
      <h2 class="mt-6 text-balance">
        Two ways in. <span class="display-italic text-ink-mid">Pick yours.</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
      <article class="group relative card-elev p-10 md:p-12 overflow-hidden hover:border-signal-phosphor/40 transition-colors duration-500 reveal">
        <!-- Subtle corner annotation -->
        <span class="absolute top-6 right-6 eyebrow !text-ink-faint">PATH · 01</span>

        <p class="eyebrow !text-signal-phosphor">FOR UTILITIES</p>
        <h3 class="mt-6 font-display text-[2rem] text-ink-paper leading-tight text-balance">
          You can't trim what<br/>
          <span class="display-italic">you can't see.</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-6 text-ink-mid">
          Ship a pilot on a 50–100 km corridor. We deliver vegetation risk maps and tier-scored alerts in your hands within 90 days. Per-km, per-year pricing.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-10 flex items-center gap-4">
          <a href={`${base}/contact?interest=pilot`} class="btn-primary">
            Book a pilot
          </a>
          <a href={`${base}/vegetation`} class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-ink-mid hover:text-ink-paper no-underline">
            Spec →
          </a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="group relative card-elev p-10 md:p-12 overflow-hidden hover:border-signal-telemetry/40 transition-colors duration-500 reveal" style="transition-delay: 100ms">
        <span class="absolute top-6 right-6 eyebrow !text-ink-faint">PATH · 02</span>

        <p class="eyebrow" style="color:#4ca7ff">FOR INVESTORS</p>
        <h3 class="mt-6 font-display text-[2rem] text-ink-paper leading-tight text-balance">
          Platform + wedge.<br/>
          <span class="display-italic">Deep-tech moat.</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-6 text-ink-mid">
          Vegetation is the revenue wedge. The twin is the long game. Grid DT proves they merge. $48B+ combined TAM, MVP shipping 2026.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-10 flex items-center gap-4">
          <a
            href={`${base}/contact?interest=investment`}
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 rounded-full border border-signal-telemetry/40 bg-signal-telemetry/10 px-6 py-3 font-medium no-underline transition-colors duration-300"
            style="color:#4ca7ff"
          >
            Request the thesis
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M1 8h13M10 3l5 5-5 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href={`${base}/about`} class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-ink-mid hover:text-ink-paper no-underline">
            About →
          </a>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
